\"someone\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Expect the closing ceremony to get high ratings.\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 365}, {\"ngram\": \"high ratings\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics, as an event, prides itself on making bizarre sports and activities look like ordinary pastimes.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"bizarre sports\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"activities\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"ordinary pastimes\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is an endless list of weird activities from Street Skateboarding to BMX, from trap shooting to fencing.\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 555, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.02946661255796e-32, \"text\": \"Skateboarding\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999998096300441, \"rank\": 1.903700249865295e-07, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an endless list\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"weird activities\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"trap shooting\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"fencing\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only other place you'd be expected to see fencing now (apart from a club) is in Bridgerton when some flaky chap \\\"insists on getting satisfaction\\\" for being dishonoured.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bridgerton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bridgerton\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bridgerton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bridgerton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only other place\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"fencing\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"a club\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"some flaky chap\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"satisfaction\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or, if you catch a repeat of The Three Musketeers, where you might see Oliver Reed brandishing a sword in anger - but only before opening time.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 811, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Three_Musketeers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.611977810482617e-41, \"text\": \"The Three Musketeers\", \"types\": [\"Q571\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Three_Musketeers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Three_Musketeers\"}, {\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oliver_Reed\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oliver Reed\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oliver_Reed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oliver_Reed\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a repeat\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"a sword\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"opening\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Air rifle shooting should go on the quaint list too, not least for the outfits they are draped in.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 