", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2329, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999998096300441, \"rank\": 1.903700249865295e-07, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How did that sport ever get through health and safety - \\\"a rider flings the bike over his head in a 360-degree flourish before realising he and the bike are plummeting to the ground and hopefully rights the wheels in time\\\".\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that sport\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"health\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2405}, {\"ngram\": \"a rider\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"his head\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"a 360-degree flourish\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"the wheels\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2565}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surfing is another sport which used to involve \\\"hanging Five\\\" or even 10 but has now been given daredevil status.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another sport\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"daredevil status\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's also being held in Tahiti at the same time -- which must make commuting from the Olympic Village quite a feat even on a jet ski.\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2715, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999999